Ask user for a year.
if it is not number -> print "Enter valid year " You can check it using year.isdigit()
If year ≤ 0, print "Year must be positive"
If divisible by 400 → print "Leap year" # Divisible means when you divide it by number there should not be any remainder you can do -> if year % 400 == 0:
Else if divisible by 100 → print "Not a leap year"
Else if divisible by 4 → print "Leap year"
Else → print "Not a leap year"
